li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Aenys_I)\" title=\"High Septon (Aenys I)\">Aenys I</a> (?–43)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pater\" title=\"Pater\">Pater</a> (43–44)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Lickspittle\" title=\"High Lickspittle\">High Lickspittle</a> (44–54)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Alfyn\" title=\"Alfyn\">Alfyn</a> (54–54/59)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(brother_of_Donnel_Hightower)\" title=\"High Septon (brother of Donnel Hightower)\">Donnel Hightower's brother</a> (54/59-?)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"High Septon (Jaehaerys I)\">Jaehaerys I</a><sup>2</sup></li>\n<li><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Dance</a> (?-129/131)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Regency_of_Aegon_III)\" title=\"High Septon (Regency of Aegon III)\">Regency</a> (129/131-143)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Aegon_III)\" title=\"High Septon (Aegon III)\">Aegon III</a> (143-?)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Baelor_I)\" title=\"High Septon (Baelor I)\">Baelor I</a> (?-161/169)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(stonemason)\" title=\"High Septon (stonemason)\">The Stonemason</a><sup>3</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(child)\" title=\"High Septon (child)\">The Child</a><sup>4</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Daeron_II)\" title=\"High Septon (Daeron II)\">Daeron II</a> (?-209/210)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Maekar_I)\" title=\"High Septon (Maekar I)\">Maekar I</a><sup>5</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Aegon_V)\" title=\"High Septon (Aegon V)\">Aegon V</a><sup>6</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Aerys_II)\" title=\"High Septon (Aerys II)\">Aerys II</a><sup>7</sup></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(fat_one)\" title=\"High Septon (fat one)\">The Fat One</a> (?–299)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Septon_(Tyrion%27s)\" title=\"High Septon (Tyrion&#39;s)\">Tyrion's</a> (299–300)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/High_Sparrow\" title=\"High Sparrow\">High Sparrow</a> (300–)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px\"><td></td></tr><tr><td scope=\"row\" class=\"navbox-group\" style=\";;\">Claimants</td><td style=\"text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;\" class=\"navbox-list navbox-even\"><div style=\"padding:0em 0.25em\">\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Moon_(septon)\" title=\"Moon (septon)\">Septon Moon</a> (~44-48)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-abovebelow\" style=\";\" colspan=\"2\"><div>\n<ul><li><sup>1</sup>Six High Septons ruled from 11 to 37 AC including him in at least <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_23_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">23</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_25_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">25&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>2</sup>Known to have been the High Septon in <a href=\"/index.php/101_AC\" title=\"101 AC\">101&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>3</sup>Known to have been the High Septon for a year in between <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_162_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">162&#160;AC</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_170_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">170&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>4</sup>Known to have been the High Septon by <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_170_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">170&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>5</sup>Known to have been the High Septon in <a href=\"/index.php/233_AC\" title=\"233 AC\">233&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>6</sup>Known to have been the High Septon in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_239_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">239&#160;AC</a></li>\n<li><sup>7</sup>Known to have been the High Septon in <a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_275_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">275&#160;AC</a></li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404000224\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.107 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.325 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1552/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 20740/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 24600/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 10087/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 2259/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.200/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.5 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  307.972      1 -total\n 74.48%  229.381      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 73.86%  227.453      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.44%   29.062     12 Template:Date\n  9.00%   27.705     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  8.97%   27.640      1 Template:High_Septons\n  8.80%   27.094      1 Template:Navbox\n  7.60%   23.414      1 Template:S-aft\n  6.99%   21.515      3 Template:Main_other\n  5.42%   16.696      1 Template:S-aft/check\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:26913-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404000224 and revision id 308259\n -->\n",
